    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Achieve More With Azure For construction"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Scalability and Flexibility"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "IoT For Smart Construction"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Data-Driven Decision-Making"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Enhanced Collaboration"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "Azure construction lets you realize the following key benefits:",
        "Deploy a scalable IT infrastructure that adapts to the changing complexity and demands of your construction projects, leading to optimal resource utilization.\n\n\n\n\nREQUEST A CALL  > >",
        "Use Azure IoT Hub and IoT Central to monitor site equipment in real-time. Ensure safe working conditions and worker health on live construction sites.\n\n\n\nREQUEST A CALL  > >",
        "Azure’s advanced analytics. ML capabilities and Power BI let you gain in-depth knowledge from historical data, real-time construction site conditions, weather forecasts, and critical construction supply chain patterns.\n\n\nREQUEST A CALL  > >",
        "The integration of Microsoft Teams and SharePoint empowers you with real-time communication and centralized document sharing that smoothens collaboration among architects, contractors, and construction project managers.\n\nREQUEST A CALL  > >"
      ],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [],
      "images": []
    },
